dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Austin Roberts. May I have your name, please?
Great, thank you, Joan. To assist you better, may I have your policy number first, please?
Yes, my policy number is eight five two four six.
Thank you, Joan. And for verification, could you please provide me with the last four digits of your social security number?
Sure, it's six five two zero.
Thank you for the information, Joan. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today regarding your policy or a claim?
I need to add a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, Joan. We can definitely assist you with that. Let's proceed with adding the new vehicle. Can you please provide me with the make and model of the vehicle you'd like to add?
Thank you, Joan. We've successfully added the 2023 Honda Accord to your policy. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
Thank you for your time, Joan. Have a great day!
